Ing '''[[Principalidad]] ning Asturias''' ([[Spanish language|Spanish]]: ''Principado de Asturias'', [[Astur-Leonese language|Asturian]]: ''Principáu d'Asturies'' o ''Asturies'') metung yang [[autonomous communities of Spain|autonomous community]] kilub ning kaarian ning [[Espanya]], dating "Kaarian ning Asturias'' inyang [[Middle Ages|Middle Ages]]. Atiu keng pangulung pampang arapan ning [[Cantabrian Dayat Malat]] (''Mar Cantábrico'', ing Kastilang lagyu oara keng [[Bay ning Biscay]]).
